title: 30: End Negative Self-Talk (Like Magic)
description:
Negative self-talk often times can be the biggest detriment to us reaching our full potential. The mind can be trained and used to produce astounding results. In this episode I teach you how to end negative self-talk for good, like magic.

Join Our Growing Community: www.kwikbrain.com
